					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">When I first started to write WedNESday back in late 2003 performance was a really big issue back then. Hardly anyone could run Nintendulator and it is only until this year that I actually rewrote the 6502 core for readability and size instead of performance.<br /><br />To be honest its such a huge waste of time to base any emulator on performance as in 3-4 years even the most demanding of emulators suddenly becomes normal.</div>

					
